Running screen 

Screen -S $name (start)
Ctrl+A, Ctrl+D -> exit the screen
Sceen -R $name (reattach)
Exit -> type inside the screen to close everything

#---------------------------------------------------------------------------#

Extract columns in specific order

awk -F "," '{ print $4, $1,$8,$7,$5,$6}' gene_data.csv
(comma is delimiter)
#---------------------------------------------------------------------------#

Merge all files into one

cat *.fna > merged_file.fna
#---------------------------------------------------------------------------#

Bash move common extension from multiple directories into one folder

mv **/*.gbk allGBKfiles/

